{
  "texts": [
    "Let j ∈ {0, 1} indicate whether a firm encourages chatbot use.",
    "Equilibrium skill prices adjust to equate the supply and demand for human capital across encouraged and non-encouraged employers.",
    "These supply and demand forces reflect workers' sorting and adoption decisions, as well as firms' encouragement and hiring policies.",
    "We characterize equilibrium skill prices in Section A.2.3.",
    "Employer encouragement."
  ]
}